data.description: COME VISIT THIS 6 BDRM 3 BATH Colonial Style home located in the Eagles Nest subdivision in Henrico County. Enter this home to find a foyer, living room which can also be used as an office or 6th bedroom, family room, spacious EIK w/plenty of wood cabinetry, LAM C/TOPS, SS APPL and tile backsplash, laundry room, full bath on 1st floor and entry to the attached finished garage complete the first level of the home. Head upstairs to find the PRIM BR w/ carpet, C/FAN, 7X5 WIC & ATT BA w/ double vanity, easy entry shower & tub for relaxing after a long day.  Continue down the hall and you will find 4 additional bedrooms w/ carpet & ample closet space, pull down attic and a shared hall bath w/ tub/shower combo & single vanity to complete the space. This home boasts beautiful HDWD throughout w/ carpet in bedrooms, Pull-down Attic storage, finished attached garage w/ epoxy floor and shelving,10X10 back deck and fenced in yard great for pets or entertaining friends & family. This home is a MUST SEE!! SCHEDULE YOUR TOUR TODAY!
